">Schnitzler an Ehrenstein, 7. 5. 1909</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01836">Schnitzler an Ehrenstein, 29. 3. 1909</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01841">Schnitzler an Ehrenstein, 7. 5. 1909</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
